{"tid":2192322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《唔撚再忍》一味講大遊行 仲有用果班！係咪仆街黎","createTime":"2020-09-07T04:54:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T00:34:02.000Z","uid":222190,"like":13,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"be7ea3fcdabc18ce31e66c1b63af013324810d18","tid":2192322,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:54:18.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\">叫人徒手出去發聲？<br />\n人多就安全？仲要咁樣 表達民意？<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">我屌你老母啦<br />\n洗乾淨對眼啦 <br />\n仲覺得係上年？</span></p><br />\n<br />\n好多人明知 今年仲用呢套係唔撚掂<br />\n好多人捨命陪君子 驚手足會出事<br />\n大家唔諗新出路 先用舊方法<br />\n係人都知 連登一早比中共滲透<br />\n<br />\n成班仆街洗板 仲叫人keep住用舊方法<br />\n另一班就屌人送頭<br />\n大家而唔係討論新出路 新方法<br />\n<span class=\"red\">乜尻子彈核彈 我地已經儲落成堆</span><br />\n<span class=\"red\">DLLM 五毛PR仆街仔 送頭理論撚</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\">我地係要新出路 </span></span>"},{"pid":"1973a14aa22225f51e570ac1d2e07f6ac90e2c8a","tid":2192322,"uid":241567,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:55:35.000Z","msg":"咁有咩提議先"},{"pid":"d49b11ac9343109aba1025f322b9fff519a9fbf4","tid":2192322,"uid":131122,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:57:38.000Z","msg":"yes，遊行無用，集會無用，出街無用，口號無用，出去係送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52da797c9ec71ef7f11c9a9f04fb3addab6c2fc2","tid":2192322,"uid":222190,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T05:00:45.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">每次遊行</span><br />\n警狗set晒陣 &gt; 未開始行 狗已經ss咬人<br />\n&gt; 手足退到商場 &gt; 開始大圍捕 &gt; <br />\n癲狗症發作(例如推跌大肚婆/扑爆頭) &gt; 手足可能轉場 癲狗症再發作&gt; be water 散場<br />\n<br />\n事後大家都好嬲post Ig FB LIHKG <br />\n外國戰線就Twitter, Reddit <br />\n<br />\n之後警謊 港共出黎9 up<br />\n大家再ig fb, 有人就寫篇野 抽下警謊水咁<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><p class=\"center\">以上事件無限輪迴</p></span><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n上年 全靠手足犧牲, 街頭抗爭<br />\n令到美帝作出制裁行動<br />\n<span class=\"red\">宜家有足夠子彈</span>(中共警暴, DQ議員, 手足受不合理對待）<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">但制裁成效 未如香港人所想</span><br />\n香港最勇武時期已經過去<br />\n<span class=\"red\">抗爭熱潮不再 唔好再昆自己</span><br />\n甚至好多人連Twitter 都冇<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span class=\"red\">點解宜家仲要 大遊行？</span><br />\n<br />\n乞求中共 有五大訴求？<br />\n儲子彈比美帝？話比人知 抗爭冇靜過？<br />\n想學白俄 烏克蘭咁勇武？<br />\n香港咁多黃絲 有幾多人肯罷工罷稅 大家一齊衝？唔通你覺得 黃碧雲會一齊衝？<br />\n每次想勇武 就同對家講埋 日期時間地點<br />\n過左成年 除左食黃店抗爭 仲可能點樣進步<br />\n唔通大家可以 韜光養晦 強身健體買裝<br />\nWe will be back?"},{"pid":"855320ffcd23cf3dbba1c45db78d0416483044db","tid":2192322,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T05:01:24.000Z","msg":"唔服既 黎屌9我"},{"pid":"879a4113d29bc771a5ed7e6945ad2a46edcf622e","tid":2192322,"uid":64702,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"855320ffcd23cf3dbba1c45db78d0416483044db","tid":2192322,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T05:01:24.000Z","msg":"唔服既 黎屌9我"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T05:02:57.000Z","msg":"出來承擔後果的人，都未講介意。如果你不能支援什麼，倒可以安靜半刻<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2192157\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2192157</a>"},{"pid":"c07c4c49d9e87c3dc9bcea142b26eedd40615358","tid":2192322,"uid":222190,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"1973a14aa22225f51e570ac1d2e07f6ac90e2c8a","tid":2192322,"uid":241567,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:55:35.000Z","msg":"咁有咩提議先"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T05:03:41.000Z","msg":"流亡政府<br />\n海外裝備<br />\n移民參軍 組師團"},{"pid":"055132a88c8d5267b8c6a36a1272ce5d7c815054","tid":2192322,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T05:05:25.000Z","msg":"我哋面臨嘅係戰爭而唔係抗爭，用